ARM: imx_v6_v7_defconfig: Select the PXP driver

The Pixel Pipeline (PXP) block is present on several i.MX SoCs
such as imx6dl, imx6sl, imx6ul, imx6sx, imx6ull and imx7d.

Select the PXP driver by default.

